    "minides": "Audi's flagship reimagined — Digital Matrix LED headlamps, predictive active suspension, Bang & Olufsen 3D sound, and quattro AWD in a long-wheelbase cabin.",
    "description": "The Audi A8 L (D5 facelift) launched in India in July 2022 in two variants: Celebration Edition and Technology. Both are exclusively long-wheelbase (LWB) and powered by a single 3.0L TFSI V6 mild-hybrid drivetrain producing 340 PS. Key features include Digital Matrix LED headlamps with animated Audi logo projections, dual 10.1-inch MMI Touch displays, a 12.3-inch Virtual Cockpit Plus cluster, 30-colour ambient lighting, Predictive Active Suspension (front camera scans road and pre-conditions suspension), quattro AWD with adaptive air suspension, four-zone climate control, and a 1,920W Bang & Olufsen Advanced Sound System with 23 speakers. The Technology variant adds rear-seat recline, rear entertainment, and the full Executive package. An armoured Security version is also available on request."
  },
